{"parse":{"title":"High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse","pageid":135382,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><figure class=\"thumb mw-halign-right show-info-icon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\" style=\"width: 150px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/6f/HGGBM_Logo.png/revision/latest?cb=20230510123339\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse Logo\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"112\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Logo.png\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Logo.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/6f/HGGBM_Logo.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20230510123339\" /></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/6f/HGGBM_Logo.png/revision/latest?cb=20230510123339\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse Logo\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/6f/HGGBM_Logo.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20230510123339\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"112\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Logo.png\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Logo.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/6f/HGGBM_Logo.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/150?cb=20230510123339\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:HGGBM_Logo.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse Logo</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure><p><b>High Grade Gundam Build Metaverse (HGGBM)</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">\u30cf\u30a4\u30b0\u30ec\u30fc\u30c9\u30ac\u30f3\u30c0\u30e0\u30d3\u30eb\u30c9\u30e1\u30bf\u30d0\u30fc\u30b9</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Hai Gur\u0113do Gandamu Birudo Metab\u0101su</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Japanese\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#00e;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is a line of <a href=\"/wiki/Gunpla\" title=\"Gunpla\">Gunpla</a> kits of the <a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Weapon\" title=\"Mobile Weapon\">Mobile Suits</a> from the <i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i> series. Like its predecessors <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Fighters\" title=\"High Grade Build Fighters\">High Grade Build Fighters</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Divers\" title=\"High Grade Build Divers\">High Grade Build Divers</a>, HGGBM includes multiple sub-lines: <b><a href=\"/wiki/Entry_Grade\" title=\"Entry Grade\">Entry Grade Gundam Build Metaverse</a> (EGGBM)</b>, <b><a href=\"/wiki/SD_Gundam_Cross_Silhouette\" title=\"SD Gundam Cross Silhouette\">SD Gundam Build Metaverse</a> (SDGBM)</b> and <b><a href=\"/wiki/Figure-rise_Standard\" title=\"Figure-rise Standard\">Figure-rise Standard Gundam Build Metaverse</a> (FRSGBM)</b>.\n</p><div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Lineup\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lineup</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lineup\">Lineup</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FHigh_Grade_Gundam_Build_Metaverse%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Regular_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Regular </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Special_Editions_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Special Editions </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Exclusives_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Exclusives </a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>HGGBM #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th>\n<th>Link\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>01 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/07/EG_Lah_Gundam_box.png/revision/latest?cb=20250307060715\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG Lah Gundam box\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/07/EG_Lah_Gundam_box.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20250307060715\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"EG Lah Gundam box.png\" data-image-key=\"EG_Lah_Gundam_box.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-78-l%C4%81-III_Lah_Gundam\" title=\"RX-78-l\u0101-III Lah Gundam\">RX-78-l\u0101-III Lah Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,000\n</td>\n<td>2023 October\n</td>\n<td>First kit in the series. First <a href=\"/wiki/Entry_Grade\" title=\"Entry Grade\">Entry Grade</a> kit to be released within a Build series. Color variant of EG-1 with additional parts. Rifle scope and backpack can be swapped with the original pieces to form a \"Nigata Type\".\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1098\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>02 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/08/EG_Build_Strike_Exceed_Galaxy_box.png/revision/latest?cb=20250307044042\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"EG Build Strike Exceed Galaxy box\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/08/EG_Build_Strike_Exceed_Galaxy_box.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20250307044042\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"EG Build Strike Exceed Galaxy box.png\" data-image-key=\"EG_Build_Strike_Exceed_Galaxy_box.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105B/EG_Build_Strike_Exceed_Galaxy\" title=\"GAT-X105B/EG Build Strike Exceed Galaxy\">GAT-X105B/EG Build Strike Exceed Galaxy</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,100\n</td>\n<td>2023 October\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of EG-2.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1099\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>03 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c1/SD_Cross_Silhouette_F-Kunoichi_Kai.png/revision/latest?cb=20231111200405\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"SD Cross Silhouette F-Kunoichi Kai\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/c1/SD_Cross_Silhouette_F-Kunoichi_Kai.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20231111200405\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"SD Cross Silhouette F-Kunoichi Kai.png\" data-image-key=\"SD_Cross_Silhouette_F-Kunoichi_Kai.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/F9%E3%83%8E1%E6%94%B9_F-Kunoichi_Kai\" title=\"F9\u30ce1\u6539 F-Kunoichi Kai\">F9\u30ce1\u6539 F-Kunoichi Kai</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2023 November\n</td>\n<td>First <a href=\"/wiki/SD_Gundam\" title=\"SD Gundam\">SD</a> release in the series. Uses <a href=\"/wiki/SD_Gundam_Cross_Silhouette\" title=\"SD Gundam Cross Silhouette\">SD Gundam Cross Silhouette</a> SD Frame and CS Frame. Parts are compatible with other <a href=\"/wiki/SD_Gundam_BB_Senshi\" title=\"SD Gundam BB Senshi\">Legend BB</a> kits for kitbashing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup>\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1102\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>04 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0e/HGGBM_Shin_Burning_Gundam_box.png/revision/latest?cb=20231111200609\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Shin Burning Gundam box\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Shin Burning Gundam box.png\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Shin_Burning_Gundam_box.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/0e/HGGBM_Shin_Burning_Gundam_box.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20231111200609\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/SBG-E01_Shin_Burning_Gundam\" title=\"SBG-E01 Shin Burning Gundam\">SBG-E01 Shin Burning Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,400\n</td>\n<td>2023 November\n</td>\n<td>First High Grade kit in the series. Parts variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Fighters\" title=\"High Grade Build Fighters\">HGBF</a>-043. Features clear orange effect parts in a pearl finish.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1103\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>05 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/84/HGGBM_Gundam_00_Diver_Arc.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20231130101154\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Gundam 00 Diver Arc\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Gundam 00 Diver Arc.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Gundam_00_Diver_Arc.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/8/84/HGGBM_Gundam_00_Diver_Arc.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20231130101154\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GN-0000DVR/II_Gundam_00_Diver_Arc\" title=\"GN-0000DVR/II Gundam 00 Diver Arc\">GN-0000DVR/II Gundam 00 Diver Arc</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,500\n</td>\n<td>2023 December\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Divers\" title=\"High Grade Build Divers\">HGBD</a>-001. Features new gimmick for GN Drive and light-absorbing resin.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1222\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>06 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b4/HGGBM_Plutine_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20231130101231\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Plutine Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Plutine Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Plutine_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b4/HGGBM_Plutine_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20231130101231\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/PFF-X7II%2B/P9_Plutine_Gundam\" title=\"PFF-X7II+/P9 Plutine Gundam\">PFF-X7II+/P9 Plutine Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,300\n</td>\n<td>2023 December\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Divers_Re:RISE\" title=\"High Grade Build Divers Re:RISE\">HGBD:R</a>-023. Pluto Armor can detach to reveal <a href=\"/wiki/PFF-X7II%2B_Core_Gundam_II_Plus\" title=\"PFF-X7II+ Core Gundam II Plus\">PFF-X7II+ Core Gundam II Plus</a>. Includes display stand for Pluto Armor. Armor is partially molded in Ecopla, which is plastic recycled from materials discarded during the production of regular Gunpla.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1223\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>07 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/7/7d/HGGBM_Typhoeus_Gundam_Chimera.jpeg/revision/latest?cb=20231209085620\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Typhoeus Gundam Chimera\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"103\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Typhoeus Gundam Chimera.jpeg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Typhoeus_Gundam_Chimera.jpeg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/7/7d/HGGBM_Typhoeus_Gundam_Chimera.jpeg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20231209085620\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/TYP-G12/CMR_Typhoeus_Gundam_Chimera\" title=\"TYP-G12/CMR Typhoeus Gundam Chimera\">TYP-G12/CMR Typhoeus Gundam Chimera</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a58,000\n</td>\n<td>2023 December\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variants of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_00\" title=\"High Grade Gundam 00\">HG00</a>-069 and Kutan Type-III from <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_IRON-BLOODED_ORPHANS\" title=\"High Grade IRON-BLOODED ORPHANS\">HGIBO</a>-007. Kutan Twin Dragon Type unit can detach to reveal <a href=\"/wiki/TYP-G12_Typhoeus_Gundam\" title=\"TYP-G12 Typhoeus Gundam\">TYP-G12 Typhoeus Gundam</a>. Includes display base. Several runners are labeled \"Psycho Gundam Mk-II\", which would later be used for <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Universal_Century\" title=\"High Grade Universal Century\">HGUC</a>-261. Armor is partially molded in Ecopla, which is plastic recycled from materials discarded during the production of regular Gunpla.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1224\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>08 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/18/HGGBM_Gundam_Perfect_Strike_Freedom_Rouge.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240109134033\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Gundam Perfect Strike Freedom Rouge\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"80\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Gundam Perfect Strike Freedom Rouge.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Gundam_Perfect_Strike_Freedom_Rouge.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/1/18/HGGBM_Gundam_Perfect_Strike_Freedom_Rouge.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240109134033\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/ZGMF-X20A-PF_Gundam_Perfect_Strike_Freedom#Variants\" title=\"ZGMF-X20A-PF Gundam Perfect Strike Freedom\">MBF-02PF Gundam Perfect Strike Freedom Rouge</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,300\n</td>\n<td>2024 January\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_Breaker_Battlogue\" title=\"High Grade Gundam Breaker Battlogue\">HGGBB</a>-03.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1289\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>09 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/62/HGGBM_Beargguy_Ohana_%26_Aloharo_Set.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240208102154\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Beargguy Ohana &amp; Aloharo Set\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"84\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Beargguy Ohana &amp; Aloharo Set.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Beargguy_Ohana_%26_Aloharo_Set.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/62/HGGBM_Beargguy_Ohana_%26_Aloharo_Set.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240208102154\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/KUMA-F_Beargguy_F#Variants\" title=\"KUMA-F Beargguy F\">Beargguy Ohana</a> &amp; Aloharo Set\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,900\n</td>\n<td>2024 February\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of HGBF-005 with color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/KUMA-F_Beargguy_F\" title=\"KUMA-F Beargguy F\">Petit'gguy</a> unit from HGBF-022 and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/Haropla\" title=\"Haropla\">HP</a>-01.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1354\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/47/FRS_Avatar_Fumina.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240318235452\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"FRS Avatar Fumina\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"83\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"FRS Avatar Fumina.jpg\" data-image-key=\"FRS_Avatar_Fumina.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/47/FRS_Avatar_Fumina.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240318235452\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Fumina_Hoshino\" title=\"Fumina Hoshino\">Avatar Fumina</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a53,800\n</td>\n<td>2024 March\n</td>\n<td>First <a href=\"/wiki/Figure-rise_Standard\" title=\"Figure-rise Standard\">Figure-rise Standard</a> release in the line. Includes three different faces, optional parts (arm and leg for equipment attachment, hair) and Rifle. Uses G-type body from 30 Minutes Sisters line.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1420\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/bd/HGGBM_Gundam_00_Command_Qan-T-_Desert_Type.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240709005612\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Gundam 00 Command Qan-T- Desert Type\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Gundam 00 Command Qan-T- Desert Type.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Gundam_00_Command_Qan-T-_Desert_Type.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/bd/HGGBM_Gundam_00_Command_Qan-T-_Desert_Type.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20240709005612\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GNT-0000SDV_Gundam_00_Command_Qan%EF%BC%BBT%EF%BC%BD\" title=\"GNT-0000SDV Gundam 00 Command Qan\uff3bT\uff3d\">GNT-0000SDV Gundam 00 Command Qan[T] Desert Type</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Metaverse\" title=\"Gundam Build Metaverse\">Gundam Build Metaverse</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a52,000\n</td>\n<td>2024 July\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of HGGBB-06.\n</td>\n<td><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://manual.bandai-hobby.net/menus/detail/1653\">Manual</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/af/HGGBM_Gundam_Amazing_Barbatos_Lupus.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20241021075052\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGGBM Gundam Amazing Barbatos Lupus\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGGBM Gundam Amazing Barbatos Lupus.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGGBM_Gundam_Amazing_Barbatos_Lupus.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/a/af/HGGBM_Gundam_Amazing_Barbatos_Lupus.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20241021075052\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a hr